nt||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|If you didn't play splinters, I would simply bid 4@H. But, since we are playing splinters, I might as well provide the extra information and bid 4@C on the way to 4@H. Now, how should terry evaluate his hand?

First of all, other than the ace, any other honor in clubs is a minus. So terry basically has a six point hand, since the K of clubs might as well be the deuce. Therefore, he has no interest in slam. However, if his K of clubs was somewhere else, say the K of diamonds or Q of hearts, then he might be more interested.|
